snippet.title: Darwin's Paradox! - Reveal Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Embark on an extraordinary adventure in Darwin's Paradox! coming to PS5 later this year. Play as Darwin, an octopus snatched from the sea and trust into a mysterious food factory, in this action adventure platformer. Wishlist now!
